{
  "stem": "14091.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This, I understood, was done to send to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were provided with materials.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were doing them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But that's all that I can really remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- mostly what I remember is the hunger, the cold, the misery, the-- the fright in everybody's eyes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And many babies used to die, because the mothers didn't have any milk or any food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they just died, and so many, so many.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they-- they were just buried, wherever we could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because we couldn't go to any cemetery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were just buried outside, like, like kittens, like-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] this what I can remember.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In June, they decided apparently that they would liquidate the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Our house was-- we can look out from the windows, across was the, the police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we knew in the afternoon that commotion began, that many, many Germans came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And also they brought from other places police and-- and so we know that something was going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But we didn't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This night, my mother and I were in the window.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We didn't sleep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it was dawn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We saw that they start coming out from that police building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they sort of divided like, in both sides.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So then we understood that they are going towards the ghetto from both sides.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And when they got closer, we let know the other people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the people start running towards the wooded area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Some of the people cut, cut apart the wire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And this is how we could start running.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "My father begged us, all of us, that we should start running.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He did not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] He decided that he will stay.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
